1 A BILL for an Act to create and enact a new section to chapter 54-03 of the North Dakota
2 Century Code, relating to legislative term limits.
3 BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATIVE ASSEMBLY OF NORTH DAKOTA:
4 SECTION 1. A new section to chapter 54-03 of the North Dakota Century Code is created
5 and enacted as follows:
6 Term limits - Calculation of years of service .
7 The time for calculating the years of service for members of the legislative assembly under
8 section 1 of article XV of the Constitution of North Dakota does not begin to run until the date on
9 which an individual is first elected or appointed to serve as a member of the legislative
10 assembly after November 7, 2022 .
